OL,7,FThe mother of a teenage boy, whose
OL,8,Fdeath will be investigated as part of
OL,9,Fthe Lampard Inquiry, told ITV News
OL,10,Fthat the introduction of effective
OL,11,Fchange will require all parties 'to
OL,12,Finsist upon it'
OL,14,FWords by James Gray, ITV News Producer
OL,16,F"We know exactly what needs to happen,
OL,17,Fthere's no mystery," says Julia
OL,18,FHopper, a mother whose teenage son's
OL,19,Fdeath was contributed to by multiple
OL,20,Ffailings in the mental health care he
OL,21,Freceived, an inquest found.
