OL,7,FHer message comes as a statutory
OL,8,Fpublic inquiry examining the deaths of
OL,9,Falmost 2,000 mental health patients in
OL,10,FEssex gets underway on Monday.
OL,12,FThe Lampard Inquiry, chaired by
OL,13,FBaroness Kate Lampard CBE, will
OL,14,Finvestigate the deaths of people who
OL,15,Fwere receiving mental health inpatient
OL,16,Fcare in Essex between 2000 and 2023.
