OL,7,FPeople who died within three months of
OL,8,Fdischarge, and those who died as
OL,9,Finpatients receiving NHS-funded care
OL,10,Fin the independent sector will be
OL,11,Fincluded in the inquiry.
OL,13,FThe Essex Mental Health Independent
OL,14,FInquiry was established in 2021
OL,15,Fwithout statutory status.
