OL,7,FIt was upgraded to a statutory footing
OL,8,Flast year, which means it has legal
OL,9,Fpowers to compel witnesses to give
OL,10,Fevidence.
OL,12,FThis came after it emerged that just
OL,13,F11 members of staff out of 14,000
OL,14,Fcontacted by the inquiry said they
OL,15,Fwould attend an evidence session.
OL,17,FMs Hopper, whose 19-year-old son,
OL,18,FChristopher Nota, died in July 2020,
OL,19,Fhas long campaigned for a public
OL,20,Finquiry, with more than 100,000
OL,21,Fsignatures collected in support.
