OL,7,FMr Nota died after falling from a
OL,8,Fheight in Southend. An inquest later
OL,9,Fconcluded that multiple significant
OL,10,Ffailures in his care contributed to
OL,11,Fhis death.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News Health
OL,14,FCorrespondent Rebecca Barry ahead of
OL,15,Fthe inquiry getting underway, Ms
OL,16,FHopper said "change must happen".
OL,18,F"But it's only through speaking to
OL,19,Fpeople like you that people can stand
OL,20,Fbehind us, stand with us and insist
OL,21,Fupon it," she said.
