OL,7,FMs Hopper continued: "The beauty of
OL,8,Fthis inquiry in Essex, if it's done
OL,9,Fproperly, is having the changes that
OL,10,Fwe need that will safeguard everybody
OL,11,Fall over our nation.
OL,13,F"And this one is the first in history.
OL,14,FLet's do it, let's do it here, let's
OL,15,Fuse this opportunity to do it
OL,16,Fproperly."
OL,18,FAfter opening statements, the inquiry
OL,19,Fis expected to move to commemorative
OL,20,Fevidence from friends and relatives
OL,21,Fabout some of those who died.
