OL,7,FIt will later move to hearing from
OL,8,Fformer patients about their
OL,9,Fexperiences.
OL,11,FMs Hopper spoke of the "huge" and
OL,12,F"textbook failings" in her son's care,
OL,13,Fexplaining that she felt "pitted as a
OL,14,Fparent against a system manned by
OL,15,Fpeople who don't care and who are free
OL,16,Fto fail".
