OL,7,F"The weight of losing Christopher is
OL,8,Fbeyond measure, but on top of that, if
OL,9,Fthat were not bad enough, is the
OL,10,Fcertainty that they knew he would die
OL,11,Fand they carelessly discharged him
OL,12,Fanyway," Ms Hopper added.
