OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "We're hoping that
OL,8,FBaroness Lampard and her inquiry team
OL,9,Fwill shine a light into all the
OL,10,Fdarkest and dustiest corners within
OL,11,Fthe Essex trusts' mental health
OL,12,Fsystems to make sure that all of the
OL,13,Ffailings, not just at the trust but
OL,14,Fmaybe at other agencies.
OL,16,F"For example, the CQC (Care Quality
OL,17,FCommission). Why did it take until
OL,18,F2020 before the CQC raised these
OL,19,Fwarnings? Why did it take 20 years?
OL,20,FWhat was the ombudsman doing?
